<script>
jQuery(document).ready(function(){
      jQuery('#toggleButton').click(function(){
        jQuery('#content').toggle(); // Toggles the visibility of the content
        // Change the button text depending on the visibility of the content
        if (jQuery('#content').is(':visible')) {
          jQuery('#toggleButton').text('Vis mindre');
        } else {
          jQuery('#toggleButton').text('Vis mer');
        }
      });
    });
  </script>
